<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <title>{{ root }} &ndash; quick url shortener</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <b>API</b> <a href="https://{{ root }}">[back]</a>
        <pre>
This service supports API calls for automation purposes.

  <b>Bash example</b>:
    $ curl -X GET 'https://{{ root }}/api?url=example.com'

  <b>Python-3 example</b>:
    1| import requests
    2| resp = requests.get('https://{{ root }}/api?url=example.com')
    3| print(resp.status_code, resp.content)

The result is returned as plain text in response.
        </pre>
    </body>
</html>
